		{
			"character": "character-1648605405.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "Upset",
			"text": "I knew who you were before you approached my shop."
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1648523040.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "Surprised",
			"text": "Ugh, was I my father's lover from another life? Yuck."
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1648605405.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "No, you dumbass! They were other people then.\nYou... You both killed me in that other life, and in this one, your father murdered my brother, my father and my mother.\nYou know that what he's got planned will do more than harm to everyone, yet, in your selfishness and in your spoils, you still hesitate about making this known."
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1648523040.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "Angry",
			"text": "He's my father!"
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1648523040.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "Sad",
			"text": "If I tell on him, not only we would lose everything, he'll go to jail too."
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1648605405.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "Upset",
			"text": "That's where he should be! For what he did to Sagrado and the rest!"
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1648523040.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "..."
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1648605405.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "Evil",
			"text": "Here you are. Unable to move. Was the drug too hard? It was the plan anyway.\nI could end your life... And avenge my family. Let your father know what it feels to lose someone.\nI could end it, and fulfil the promise Isabela made... That I made in my previous life. \nOver hundreds of lives we've destroyed ourselves. Why could we not add fuel to that fire?"
		},
